</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d155n1-ptr" id="PJA13d155n1">1</a>

   <p>For <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s refusal to send Mazzeis <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-13-02-0080" class="document">28 June</a> letter to America and his reasons for it, see his reply to Mazzei of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-13-02-0143" class="document">12 Aug.</a>, below.</p>

